{"tid":1558084,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"（發大黎講）有建制派/中國官方預警911有人將發動恐怖襲擊","createTime":"2019-09-10T10:44:49.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-10T10:54:04.000Z","uid":51200,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"ca16a6790fece7e8c54c1af63134419e40e64705","tid":1558084,"uid":51200,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-10T10:44:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/NdC0jAe.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FNdC0jAe.jpg&h=e966a55f&s={SIZE}\" /> <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/1rn7J1W.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F1rn7J1W.png&h=eb518865&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<br />\n我懷疑有人同恐怖組織有聯繫<br />\n所以先至可以預言到有人會係9月11號發動恐怖襲擊<br />\n有冇人可以幫手報警<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n如果聽日真係有啦恐怖襲擊出現<br />\n唔排除係呢班人勾結恐怖組織發動襲擊<br />\n<br />\n老老實實我真係未聽過美國911之前塔利班有預警過<br />\n除非佢哋本人係恐怖分子<br />\n如果唔係理論上應該無人知道會係邊日同咩地方發動襲擊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n陸頌雄Facebook 仲要用美國911做背景<br />\n有冇人可以主動同美國傳媒傾下"},{"pid":"523662c7bc3b40e85bed140d520e6423ad10464c","tid":1558084,"uid":51200,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-10T10:46:37.000Z","msg":"Up"},{"pid":"dd15d351453a38f2fe37bec8b1cbf96b552aea4f","tid":1558084,"uid":51200,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-10T10:50:06.000Z","msg":"Up"},{"pid":"e6c9ff4037e5dccb681d0fd1ca50798fce321d04","tid":1558084,"uid":58335,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-10T10:52:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d0e8e4fefff52ad9f861d46bd17fa82a807b971f","tid":1558084,"uid":270327,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-10T10:54:04.000Z","msg":"戒嚴囉屌！"}]}